Pokedex

Egg group - GRASS

As it drowses the day away, it nourishes itself by sucking from tree roots. It wakens at the fall of night, wandering off in search of a new tree.
Places where Shiinotic lives are treacherous to enter at night. People confused by its strange lights can never find their way home again.
